ihanoukville (city)]]|the province|[[Sihanoukville Province]]}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Sihanoukville Municipality\n| other_name              = Krong Sihanoukville\n| native_name             = \u1780\u17d2\u179a\u17bb\u1784\u1796\u17d2\u179a\u17c7\u179f\u17b8\u17a0\u1793\u17bb<br>''Krong Preah Sihanouk''\n| native_name_lang        = km\n| settlement_type         = [[List of Cambodian districts and sections|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = \n| flag_alt                = \n| image_seal              = \n| seal_alt                = \n| image_shield            = \n| shield_alt              = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = Sihanoukville_Province_Districts_Map_2014.png\n| mapsize                 = 276px\n| map_caption             = '''[[Preah Sihanouk Province]] districts:<br>Krong Preah Sihanouk (dark red), [[Stueng Hav]] (yellow), [[Prey Nob]] (blue), [[Kampong Seila]] (green)'''\n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = \n| coor_pinpoint           = \n| coordinates_footnotes   =  \n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = [[Cambodia]]\n| subdivision_type1       = [[Provinces of Cambodia|Province]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Preah Sihanouk Province]]\n| subdivision_type2       = \n| subdivision_name2       = \n| subdivision_type3       = \n| subdivision_name3       = \n| established_title       = \n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| seat_type               = \n| seat                    = \n| government_footnotes    = \n| leader_party            = \n| leader_title            = \n| leader_name             = \n| unit_pref               = Metric<!-- or US or UK -->\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = \n| area_land_km2           = \n| area_water_km2          = \n| area_water_percent      = \n| area_note               = \n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| population_total        = \n| population_as_of        = \n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      = \n| population_note         = \n| timezone1               = [[Time in Cambodia|ICT]]\n| utc_offset1             = +7\n| timezone1_DST           = \n| utc_offset1_DST         = \n| postal_code_type        = \n| postal_code             = 18000\n| area_code_type          = \n| area_code               = 034\n| iso_code                = \n| website                 = {{URL|http://sihanoukville.gov.kh/en/}}\n| blank_name              = Geocode\n| blank_info              = 1801\n| footnotes               = \n}}\n\n'''Preah Sihanouk Municipality''' is one of four districts of [[Preah Sihanouk Province]] in [[Cambodia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stat.go.jp/info/meetings/cambodia/pdf/18com_11.pdf| title=Map 18. Administrative Areas in Preah Sihanouk Province by District and Commune|publisher=National Institute of Statistics, Ministry of Planning (Cambodia) |date=2013-12-31}}</ref>  In 1998, it had an urban population of 67,440.<ref>{{Cite web | title = General Population Census of Cambodia 1998, Final Census Results\n| publisher = National Institute of Statistics, Ministry of Planning, Cambodia | date = August 2002 | url = http://www.nis.gov.kh/nis/uploadFile/pdf/CensusResult98.pdf\n| accessdate = 2010-11-24|page=231}}</ref> In addition to [[Sihanoukville City]] and [[Sihanoukville Autonomous Port]], the islands Koh Puos, Koh Preab, Koh Doung, Koh Kaong Kang, Koh Tres, Koh Koun, Koh Tuich, [[Koh Rong]], and [[Koh Rong Sanloem]] are under Krong Preah Sihanouk administration.<ref>http://www.stat.go.jp/info/meetings/cambodia/pdf/18com_m2.pdf</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.visitkohrong.com/a-list-of-cambodian-islands/|title=A List of Cambodian Islands|date=2019-10-26|website=Visit Koh Rong|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-12}}</ref>\n\n<center>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; margin: auto; font-weight:600; width:60%\"\n! colspan=\"22\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:110%; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|The communes of Krong Preah Sihanouk District\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|ISO Code\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|Commune\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|Romanization\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|Population\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|Sections\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#483d8b; color:#fff;\"|Urban\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 180101\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| \u179f\u1784\u17d2\u1780\u17b6\u178f\u17cb\u1798\u17bd\u1799\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| Sangkat Muoy\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 37,440\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 3\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| Yes\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 180102\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| \u179f\u1784\u17d2\u1780\u17b6\u178f\u17cb\u1796\u17b8\u179a \n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| Sangkat Pir\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 25,142\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 3\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| Yes\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| 180103\n!style=\"text-align:center; background:#dc143c; color:#fff;\"| \u179f\u1784\u17